'''Kolme'starn''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of [[Bothawui/Legends|Bothawui]]. 

It was located in the midlands of the [[Planet/Legends|planet's]] western continent, situated between [[Odve'starn]] (to the west) and the [[capital/Legends|capital]] of [[Drev'starn]] (to the east).

